<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Job Opportunity</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #4a4a4a;">New Job Opportunity</h1>
        <p>Hello {{candidateEmail}},</p>
        <p>We have a new job opportunity that matches your profile:</p>
        <div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-top: 0;">{{job.jobTitle}}</h2>
            <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{job.company.companyName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Experience Level:</strong> {{job.experienceLevel}}</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
            <p>{{job.jobDescription}}</p>
            <p><strong>Application Deadline:</strong> {{job.endDate}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>If you're interested in this position, please log in to your account to apply or contact the company directly.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Job Board Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
